Bay Ridge parkway, at Third Ave.  The street running east and west under the bridge, is the Bay Ridge Parkway.  Overhead is Third Ave., running north and south; the Third Ave., Elevated Line of the B.M.T. is seen above it.

About 1915.

Eugene L. Arbruster Collection.
